(320, 22, 'multiple_choice', 'Which  TWO  of the following statements are true of the researchers at London Zoo?', '["A. They are hoping to expand the numbers of different corals being bred in laboratories.","B. They want to identify corals that can cope well with the changed sea conditions.","C. They are looking at ways of creating artificial reefs that corals could grow on.","D. They are trying out methods that would speed up reproduction in some corals.","E. They are investigating materials that might protect reefs from higher temperatures."]', 'B. They want to identify corals that can cope well with the changed sea conditions.', NULL, NULL, 1, '"identifying hardy coral species that could survive in warmer, more acidic waters."', NOW());
