(20044, 31, 'fill_blank', NULL, NULL, 'rats', NULL, '[note]\n# Research in the area around the Chembe Bird Sanctuary\n## The importance of birds of prey to the local communities\n● They destroy {Q31} and other rodents.\n● They help to prevent farmers from being bitten by {Q32}\n● They have been an important part of the local culture for many years.\n● They now support the economy by encouraging {Q33} in the area.\n## Falling numbers of birds of prey\n● The birds may be accidentally killed\n○ by {Q34} when they are hunting or sleeping\n○ by electrocution from contact with power lines, especially at times when there is a lot of {Q35}\n● Local farmers may illegally shoot them or {Q36} them.\n## Ways of protecting chickens from birds of prey\n● clearing away vegetation from the area (unhelpful)\n● providing a {Q37} for chickens (expensive)\n● frightening birds of prey by\n○ keeping a {Q38}\n○ making a {Q39} – e.g. with metal objects\n● A {Q40} of methods is usually most effective.', 1, NULL, NOW());
